            "msg_string": "Haah... It's finally over. I'm totally beat."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, I'm still not used to this either..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Oskar and Harol? This is an unusual combination to see."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Hey, Sophie. We just happened to have a meeting. We're on our way back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "A meeting?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Representatives from many stores gathered together, and talked about recent news and other situations."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "...Although there isn't a need to talk THAT much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "My mom was really busy today, so I had to go in her place."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I didn't know there were meetings like that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "...Wait? Did I need to go to this meeting too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Your shop isn't a member of our association, so you didn't need to go. You were never invited before, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, that's right..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "It's a meeting for stores in a certain area. Not everyone is called to attend."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Your place is a little distant, so you're outside of the area."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I didn't know. That's good, though."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "By the way, what happened there?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I can't really say anything happened. It was all the same as usual."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "It's better if there aren't any problems. Anyway, I'm going now."
        }
    ]
